author: The Lunduke Journal
description:
Adobe filed a fraudulent Copyright Claim (via YouTube) in order to silence critical reporting from The Lunduke Journal. Now Adobe has 10 days to take legal action.

One of the videos Adobe filed a fraudulent claim against (containing statements from Adobe's CEO and CPO on ending DEI policies):
https://x.com/LundukeJournal/status/1914160985977335942

https://lunduke.com/
title: Counter Claim Filed Against Adobe's Efforts to Silence Journalist
